path></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container>其中的任意一项，直到数列中仅剩下一个数24为止。</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目分析\"><a href=\"#题目分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目分析\"></a>题目分析</h3><p>思路其实很简单….</p>\n<p>首先我们知道，对于数列和超过24的情况，我们可以先用部份数凑出一个24，多出来的数相邻两项两两相减得1，随后使1与24相乘即可。</p>\n<p>对于数列和小于24的情况，显然不好处理，同时显然我们可以直接凑一个结果输出出来….​</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\n#define int long long\n#define maxn 100005\nusing namespace std;\nint n;\nsigned main() {\n\tcin&gt;&gt;n;\n\tif (n == 1 || n == 2 || n == 3) {\n\t\tputs(\"NO\");\n\t\treturn 0;\n\t} else if (n == 4) {\n\t\tputs(\"YES\");\n\t\tputs(\"4 * 3 = 12\");\n\t\tputs(\"2 * 1 = 2\");\n\t\tputs(\"12 * 2 = 24\");\n\t\treturn 0;\n\t} else if (n == 5) {\n\t\tputs(\"YES\");\n\t\tputs(\"5 * 4 = 20\");\n\t\tputs(\"3 + 2 = 5\");\n\t\tputs(\"5 - 1 = 4\");\n\t\tputs(\"20 + 4 = 24\");\n\t\treturn 0;\n\t} else if (n == 6) {\n\t\tputs(\"YES\");\n\t\tputs(\"5 * 6 = 30\");\n\t\tputs(\"2 * 4 = 8\");\n\t\tputs(\"30 - 8 = 22\");\n\t\tputs(\"22 + 3 = 25\");\n\t\tputs(\"25 - 1 = 24\");\n\t\treturn 0;\n\t}\n\tint ans = n;\n\tint times;\n\tputs(\"YES\");\n\tfor (register int i = n - 1; i &gt;= 1 &amp;&amp; ans != 24; i--) {\n\t\ttimes = i;\n\t\tif (ans &gt; 24) {\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; \" - \" &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; \" = \" &lt;&lt; ans - i &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\t\tans -= i;\n\t\t} else if (ans &lt; 24) {\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; \" + \" &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; \" = \" &lt;&lt; ans + i &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\t\tans += i;\n\t\t} else\n\t\t\tbreak;\n\t}\n\ttimes--;\n\t//cout &lt;&lt; \"times:\" &lt;&lt; times &lt;&lt; endl;\n\tif (times % 2 == 1) {\n\t\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; \" * \" &lt;&lt; 1 &lt;&lt; \" = \" &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\tfor (register int i = times - 1; i &gt;= 2; i -= 2) {\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; i + 1 &lt;&lt; \" - \" &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; \" = 1\\n\";\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; \" * 1 = \" &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\t}\n\t} else {\n\t\tfor (register int i = times - 1; i &gt;= 1; i -= 2) {\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; i + 1 &lt;&lt; \" - \" &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; \" = 1\\n\";\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; \" * 1 = \" &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn 0;\n}</code></pre>\n\n","text":"CF的题总能给我一些意料之外的惊喜呢🤬 题意概括给定一个数n，要求使用1,2,3,….,n的数列，每次取其中两个数，记作a、b，将他们从原数列中删除，并在数列中插入、、其中的任意一项，直到数列中仅剩下一个数24为止。 题目分析思路其实很简单…. 首先我们知道，对于数列和超过24的...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":33,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CodeForces","slug":"CodeForces","count":13,"path":"api/tags/CodeForces.json"},{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":23,"path":"api/tags/恢复OI实力.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E6%84%8F%E6%A6%82%E6%8B%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题意概括</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目分析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"白泽","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"一个正在追逐游戏开发梦的大学生！","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/Bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/91730547"},"zhihu":{"icon":"/svg/Zhihu.svg","link":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/ying-zong-pai-wu-seng"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"CF1175A-From Hero to Zero","uid":"d549c1b82ed29c9c7e3d9963ff8b0c1d","slug":"CF1175A","date":"2021-08-10T04:16:28.000Z","updated":"2021-08-10T12:42:15.105Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CF1175A.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"te